{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"style","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/style","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>style&nbsp;</code></strong>属性指定了指定其元素的样式信息。它的功能与 HTML 中的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/style\">style</a>属性相同。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用环境","title":"使用环境","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Categories</th>\n   <td>Presentation attribute</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td>&lt;style&gt;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Normative document</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/styling.html#StyleAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"style\">&lt;style&gt;</dt>\n <dd>样式数据的语法取决于样式表语言。默认情况下，如果未指定&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/contentStyleType\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">contentStyleType (en-US)</a></code>，样式表语言为 CSS。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下示例展示了使用 CSS 作为样式表语言来使用 style 属性，为一个矩形框添加样式。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewbox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 1000 500<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rect</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>600<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>200<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">fill</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">stroke</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">stroke-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用 style 属性</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#container\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Container\">Container elements</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#filterprimitive\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#FilterPrimitive\">Filter primitive elements</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#gradient\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Gradient\">Gradient elements</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#graphics\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Graphics\">Graphics elements</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#structural\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Structural\">Structural elements</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#textcontent\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#TextContent\">Text content elements</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/clipPath\"><code>&lt;clipPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font\"><code>&lt;font&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关","title":"相关","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用环境","id":"使用环境"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"相关","id":"相关"}],"summary":"« SVG Attribute reference home","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"style","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"style","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"style","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/style","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/style/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/style","title":"style"}],"pageTitle":"style - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}